  12,86,"qal yaequb mjybana lhm: la 'azhar hmmi wahuzni 'iilaa lilah whdh, fahu kashif aldrr walbla', wa'aelam min rahmat allah wfrjh ma la telmwnh"
  12,87,"qal yeqwb: ya abnayy ewdu 'iilaa \"msr\" fastqsu 'akhbar yusif wakhyh, wala tqteu rja'km min rahmat allh, 'iinah la yaqtae alraja' min rahmat allah 'iilaa aljahdwn lqdrth, alkafirun bh"
  12,88,"fdhhbu 'iilaa \"msr\", falamaa dakhaluu ealaa yusif qalu: ya 'ayuha aleaziz asabna wa'ahlana alqht waljdb, wjynak bithaman rdy' qlyl, faetna bih ma kunt tetyna min qibal balthmn aljyd, wtsddaq ealayna bqbd hadhih aldrahm almzjat wtjwwaz fyha, 'iina allah taealaa ythyb almtfddilyn ela ahl alhajat bamwalhm"
