  12,90,"qalu: a'innak la'ant ywsf? qal: nem 'ana ywsf, whdha shqyqy, qad tfddal allah elyna, fajamae baynana baed alfrqt, 'iinah man yataq allh, wayasbir ealaa almhn, fa'iina allah la yadhhab thawab 'ihsanh, wa'iinama yjzyh 'ahsan aljza'"
